, female genitalia: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[884,909,1846,1870]" pageId="19" pageNumber="174">78</emphasis>
. Ventral view; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1067,1092,1846,1870]" pageId="19" pageNumber="174">79</emphasis>
