<emphasis bold="true" box="[215,240,1882,1906]" pageId="19" pageNumber="174">80</emphasis>
. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[622,647,1882,1906]" pageId="19" pageNumber="174">81</emphasis>
