<paragraph blockId="20.[151,1437,151,933]" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">
Male terminalia (
<figureCitation box="[392,522,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 71–77</figureCitation>
). Pygofer subtriangular in lateral view, posterior margin with short triangular protuberance on each side in the middle region (
<figureCitation box="[652,736,187,213]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Fig. 71</figureCitation>
); medioventral process of pygofer conspicuous in lateral view, with posterior margin triangular in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[709,842,223,249]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 71, 73</figureCitation>
). Gonostyli with rather truncated apex in lateral and dorsal view (
<figureCitation box="[295,425,258,285]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 74, 75</figureCitation>
); basal half narrow and slightly widened in the middle, distal half wider and divergent apically in dorsal and posterior views (
<figureCitation box="[546,676,294,321]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 73, 75</figureCitation>
). Phallic complex (
<figureCitation box="[889,1020,295,322]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 76–77</figureCitation>
): periandrium almost straight bearing one slender, elongated, and straight spine anteriorly directed (S1), and one slender, elongated, slightly curved spine anteroventrally directed (S2); aedeagus narrow, widening distally with two spines: one short, slender, in the median region (S3), and one short, slender, near the apex (S4). Anal tube with dorsal margin almost straight; base of the anal tube long, approximately 2 times length of anal tube extension in lateral view; anal tube extension abruptly folded ventrally at apex in lateral view, apex smoothly reentrant in posterior view (
<figureCitation box="[999,1131,475,501]" captionStart="FIGURES 71–77" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1784,1808]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1755]" captionTargetId="figure-24@18.[151,1435,181,1760]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 71–77. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., male genitalia: 71. Genital capsule, lateral view; 72. Anal tube and pygofer, dorsal view; 73. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; 74. Gonostylus left lateral view; 74. Gonostyli, dorsal view; 75. Phallic complex, left lateral view 67.Phallic complex, right lateral view. Scale bars: 71, 73 = 0.2 mm; 72, 74–77 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405041" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405041/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 71–73</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="20.[151,1437,151,933]" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">
Female terminalia (
<figureCitation box="[420,552,511,537]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 78–83</figureCitation>
). Pygofer elongate, symmetrical, about 3 times longer than the greatest width in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[340,426,547,573]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Fig. 78</figureCitation>
). Gonoplac (third valvula) longer than wide, apex rounded in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[1286,1372,547,573]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Fig. 79</figureCitation>
). Gonapophysis IX (second valvula) strongly sclerotized dorsally, tapered towards apex (
<figureCitation box="[1109,1195,583,609]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Fig. 80</figureCitation>
); with approximately 13 denticles (de) at distal 1/3 (
<figureCitation box="[490,574,619,645]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Fig. 82</figureCitation>
). Gonapophysis VIII (first valvula) longer than wide, slender, slightly curved upwards (
<figureCitation box="[261,391,655,681]" captionStart="FIGURES 78–83" captionStartId="19.[151,264,1846,1870]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,711,1822]" captionTargetId="figure-278@19.[151,1435,705,1822]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 78–83. Bennarella maculipennis sp. nov., female genitalia: 78. Ventral view; 79. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; 80. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 81. Gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula); 82. Apex of the gonapophysis IX (second valvula); 83. Apex of the gonapophysis VIII, lateral view (first valvula). Scale bars: 78 = 0.2 mm; 79–83 = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405045/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="175">Figs 81, 83</figureCitation>
